          <div className="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-green-100">
            <h4 className="text-green-800 font-bold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>💡</span> Como Funciona
            </h4>
            <ul className="text-sm text-green-700 space-y-2 list-disc pl-4">
              <li>Selecione sua tabela no Excel (incluindo o cabeçalho).</li>
              <li>Pressione <strong>Ctrl+C</strong>.</li>
              <li>Clique na caixa abaixo e pressione <strong>Ctrl+V</strong>.</li>
              <li>O sistema identifica as NRs automaticamente (ex: NR-6, NR-12).</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div className="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-blue-100">
            <h4 className="text-blue-800 font-bold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>📋</span> Colunas Recomendadas
            </h4>
            <p className="text-xs text-blue-700 leading-relaxed">
              Nome Completo, Matrícula, Função, Setor, NR-5, NR-6, NR-10, NR-12, NR-35...
              <br/><br/>
              <em>* Use datas no formato AAAA-MM-DD ou DD/MM/AAAA.</em>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div className="relative">
          <textarea
            className="w-full h-80 p-6 border-2 border-gray-100 rounded-3xl font-mono text-sm outline-none focus:border-green-500 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-green-500/10 transition-all bg-gray-50/50"
            placeholder="Cole aqui os dados copiados da sua planilha..."
            value={inputText}
            onChange={(e) => setInputText(e.target.value)}
          />
          {inputText === '' && (
            <div className="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none opacity-20 flex-col">
              <span className="text-6xl mb-2">📄</span>
