          <p className="text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest">Sincronize sua Planilha em Tempo Real</p>
        </header>

        <div className="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div className="space-y-6">
            <h3 className="text-lg font-black text-gray-800 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span className="text-green-500">1.</span> Preparar o Google Script
            </h3>
            <p className="text-xs text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
              Vá em <b>Extensões > Apps Script</b> na sua planilha e cole o código abaixo. Depois, <b>Implante como App da Web</b> acessível por <b>"Qualquer pessoa"</b>.
            </p>

            <div className="relative group">
              <pre className="bg-gray-900 text-green-400 p-6 rounded-2xl text-[10px] font-mono overflow-hidden h-48 border-2 border-gray-800 group-hover:border-green-500 transition-all">
                {scriptCode}
              </pre>
              <button 
                onClick={copyToClipboard}
                className="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-green-500 transition-all shadow-lg"
              >
                Copiar Código
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div className="space-y-6">
            <h3 className="text-lg font-black text-gray-800 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span className="text-green-500">2.</span> Conectar ao App
            </h3>

            <div className="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <label className="block text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase mb-2 tracking-widest ml-1">URL da Implantação (App da Web)</label>
                <input 
                  type="text" 
                  className={`w-full bg-gray-50 border-2 rounded-2xl p-4 outline-none transition-all text-sm font-mono ${
                    status === 'error' ? 'border-red-200 focus:border-red-500' : 'border-gray-100 focus:border-green-500'
                  }`}
                  placeholder="https://script.google.com/macros/s/.../exec"
                  value={url}
                  onChange={(e) => {
                    setUrl(e.target.value);
                    setStatus('idle');
                  }}
                />
              </div>

              <button 
                onClick={validateAndTest}
                disabled={status === 'testing' || !url}
                className={`w-full py-5 rounded-2xl font-black tracking-widest text-xs transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3 ${
                  status === 'testing' ? 'bg-gray-100 text-gray-400' :
                  status === 'success' ? 'bg-green-600 text-white shadow-xl shadow-green-900/20' :
                  status === 'error' ? 'bg-red-500 text-white' :
                  'bg-[#064E3B] text-green-400 hover:bg-green-900 shadow-xl shadow-green-900/10'
                }`}
              >
                {status === 'testing' ? 'VALIDANDO CONEXÃO...' : 
                 status === 'success' ? 'CONEXÃO ESTABELECIDA ✅' : 
                 status === 'error' ? 'FALHA NA CONEXÃO 🔄' : 
                 'TESTAR E SALVAR CONFIGURAÇÃO'}
              </button>

              {status === 'error' && (
                <div className="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-red-100">
                  <p className="text-red-700 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-tight mb-1">Erro identificado:</p>
                  <p className="text-red-600 text-xs font-medium leading-relaxed">{errorMessage}</p>
                </div>
              )}

              {status === 'success' && testResult && (
                <div className="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-green-100 animate-fadeIn">
                  <p className="text-green-800 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-tight mb-2">Tudo Certo! 🚀</p>
                  <div className="flex gap-4">
                    <div className="bg-white p-3 rounded-xl border border-green-200/50 flex-1">
                      <p className="text-[9px] text-gray-400 uppercase font-black">Registros Lidos</p>
                      <p className="text-xl font-black text-green-700">{testResult.count}</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              )}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div className="bg-amber-50 p-8 rounded-[3rem] border border-amber-100 flex items-center gap-6">
        <div className="text-4xl">💡</div>
        <div>
          <h4 className="text-xs font-black text-amber-800 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Dica de Especialista</h4>
          <p className="text-[11px] text-amber-700 font-bold leading-relaxed">
            Se você alterar qualquer coisa no código do Google Script, você <b>PRECISA</b> criar uma "Nova Versão" na tela de implantação, caso contrário o Google continuará servindo o código antigo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

export default ConfigView;

